description: A Chitauri invasion means the Avengers Alliance is going to need reinforcements! Nova, Ms. Marvel, and Squirrel Girl join the fray—with a special appearance by the Guardians of the Galaxy! Don’t miss part 2 of this exclusive 4-part series, bridging the story from the smash hit mobile game Marvel: Avengers Alliance and the upcoming massive sequel, Marvel: Avengers Alliance 2!
name: The Time is Now

description:

  • News Team - Meet the Team! (Alan Hebden - Jose Ortiz) (from Eagle issue 100)
  • News Team - Kidnapping the President (Alan Hebden - Jose Ortiz) (from Eagle 101 to 103)
